description: This file contains backend API implementations and data handling logic for WiFi configuration management, including getter and setter functions for various WiFi parameters, radio and regional settings, and related operations. It appears to be part of a larger system that manages WiFi devices in a TR-181 (CWMP) data model context.

methods.name: Radio_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves integer parameter value for a given radio parameter, such as MCS, TransmitPower, user controls, channel, bandwidth, and various thresholds. It uses context handle to identify the radio instance and returns TRUE on success.

methods.name: Radio_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameter value for the radio, including operational metrics like uptime, last change, supported frequency bands, channel info, and other radio state variables.

methods.name: Radio_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameters such as Alias, Name, OperatingFrequencyBand, SupportedStandards, and supported DataRates for a radio configuration.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets boolean parameters on the radio, including Enable, AutoChannelEnable, IEEE80211hEnabled, DfsEnabled, DCSEnabled, and multiple wireless features. Checks for validity and imposes constraints such as radio presence and force disable flags.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets integer parameters on the radio, such as MCS, TransmitPower, user controls, extension channels, guard intervals, thresholds, and beacon intervals. Includes validation for channel and bandwidth compatibility.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Configures ULONG parameters such as channel, bandwidth, RTS/fragmentation thresholds, etc. Checks for operational validity and consistency.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets string parameters such as Alias, RegulatoryDomain, SupportedStandards, DataRates, and OperatingStandards. Performs validation and updates global configuration for region settings.

methods.name: isValidTransmitRate
methods.description: Validates a transmit rate string to contain only digits, commas, and dots.

methods.name: Radio_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves integer parameter values for radio settings such as MCS, TransmitPower, channel, bandwidth, thresholds, etc., based on radio instance context.

methods.name: Radio_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters related to radio metrics and states, including uptime, supported bands, etc.

methods.name: Radio_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameters such as Alias, Name, OperatingFrequencyBand, SupportedStandards, etc.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets boolean radio parameters like Enable, AutoChannelEnable, IEEE80211hEnabled, etc., with validation.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets integer radio parameters such as MCS, TransmitPower, extension channels, thresholds, etc., with validation.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Configures ULONG parameters such as channel, bandwidth, RTS/fragmentation thresholds, with validation.

methods.name: Radio_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets string parameters like Alias, RegulatoryDomain, SupportedStandards, DataRates, etc., performing necessary validation.

methods.name: isValidTransmitRate
methods.description: Validates transmit rate strings to contain only digits, commas, and dots.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameter value for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameter value for Post Association Discovery, including thresholds and sampling parameters.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets boolean parameters for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets integer parameters for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets ULONG parameters for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets string parameters such as thresholds and sampling intervals for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_Validate
methods.description: Validates the configuration before commit for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_Commit
methods.description: Commits the changes for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: PostAssocDisc_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back changes for Post Association Discovery.

methods.name: WPS_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves boolean values for WPS parameters like Enable.

methods.name: WPS_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves integer values for WPS parameters like X_CISCO_COM_WpsPushButton.

methods.name: WPS_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG values (not supported) for WPS.

methods.name: WPS_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameters such as ConfigMethodsSupported, ConfigMethodsEnabled, and Pin for WPS.

methods.name: WPS_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets boolean parameters for WPS like Enable, ActivatePushButton, CancelSession.

methods.name: WPS_SetParamIntValue
methods.description: Sets integer parameters for WPS, such as WpsPushButton.

methods.name: WPS_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets string parameters for WPS including ConfigMethodsEnabled, and Pin.

methods.name: WPS_Validate
methods.description: Validates conditions (like WPS is enabled and security modes) before committing WPS settings.

methods.name: WPS_Commit
methods.description: Finalizes WPS settings, including activating push button if requested.

methods.name: WPS_Rollback
methods.description: Rolls back WPS settings if validation fails.

methods.name: IsValidMacAddress
methods.description: Checks whether a string is a valid MAC address in proper format.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves boolean parameters related to Interworking, e.g., Internet, ASRA, ESR, UESA.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_GetParamIntValue
methods.description: Retrieves integer parameters related to Interworking, unimplemented here.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves ULONG parameters like AccessNetworkType for Interworking.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_GetParamStringValue
methods.description: Retrieves string parameters such as HESSID for Interworking.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets boolean parameters for Interworking, e.g., Internet, ASRA, ESR, UESA, VenueOptionPresent, HESSOptionPresent.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Supports setting ULONG parameters like AccessNetworkType for Interworking.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_SetParamStringValue
methods.description: Sets string parameters like HESSID for Interworking.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_Venue_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves venue info parameters: Type and Group.

methods.name: InterworkingElement_Venue_SetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Sets venue info parameters: Type and Group.

methods.name: GASConfig_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns the number of GAS configuration entries.

methods.name: GASConfig_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves specific GAS configuration entry by index.

methods.name: GASConfig_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Retrieves boolean value for GAS configuration parameter: PauseForServerResponse.

methods.name: GASConfig_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves unsigned long GAS configuration parameters: AdvertisementID, ResponseTimeout, ComeBackDelay, ResponseBufferingTime, QueryResponseLengthLimit.

methods.name: GASStats_GetEntryCount
methods.description: Returns count of GAS statistics entries.

methods.name: GASStats_GetEntry
methods.description: Retrieves a GAS statistics entry by index, but here it returns NULL.

methods.name: GASStats_GetParamUlongValue
methods.description: Retrieves various ULONG statistics: AdvertisementID, Queries, QueryRate, Responses, ResponseRate, NoRequestOutstanding, ResponsesDiscarded, FailedResponses.

methods.name: MacFilter_GetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Checks if MAC filtering is enabled and whether it is set as blacklist or whitelist.

methods.name: MacFilter_SetParamBoolValue
methods.description: Sets MAC filter enable or mode (blacklist/whitelist).
